277
00:14:19,692 --> 00:14:23,320
Permisi, akan kucari di Google
cara beli kartu kredit.

278
00:14:31,120 --> 00:14:33,581
Kukira aku cuma akan beli dua Frappuccino

279
00:14:33,664 --> 00:14:35,666
