280
00:14:36,083 --> 00:14:37,084
Jangan pelit.

281
00:14:37,167 --> 00:14:40,921
Jika obrolannya begitu mendesak,
traktir minum pacar kami juga.

282
00:14:41,005 --> 00:14:43,507
Baiklah. Kenapa robot butuh kopi?

283
00:14:44,717 --> 00:14:47,928
