284
00:14:48,554 --> 00:14:49,847
Silakan, Gears.

285
00:14:49,930 --> 00:14:52,433
Terima kasih. Astaga, aku haus.

286
00:14:52,516 --> 00:14:53,684
Jadi, ada apa ini?

287
00:14:53,767 --> 00:14:56,896
Dari blazermu, kau terkesan
akan menjerat kami ke skema piramida.

288
00:14:56,979 --> 00:14:58,022
Jadi, ada apa?

289
00:14:58,772 --> 00:15:00,482
Aku sangat mencemaskan Devi.

290
00:15:00,566 --> 00:15:02,401
Dengar, maafkan aku, Ben,

291
00:15:02,484 --> 00:15:04,778
