untuk menaburkan abu ayahnya hari ini.

298
00:15:23,339 --> 00:15:24,340
Benarkah?

299
00:15:24,423 --> 00:15:27,718
Kalian lebih mengenal Devi.
Hanya kalian yang akan dia dengarkan.

300
00:15:28,510 --> 00:15:29,595
Kalian mau membantu?

301
00:15:34,642 --> 00:15:37,353
Ya ampun. Nikmat sekali.

302
00:15:43,901 --> 00:15:46,445
Devi menelepon.
Dia ingin bekerja denganku di Old Navy.

303
00:15:46,528 --> 00:15:47,613
Bagus, 'kan?

304
00:15:48,155 --> 00:15:49,281
Ya, tentu.

305
00:15:49,865 --> 00:15:51,867
Kenapa dia sudah lama tak mampir?

306
00:15:52,493 --> 00:15:53,994
Katamu kalian berciuman.

307
00:15:54,620 --> 00:15:57,581
- Banyak yang kucium.
- Ya, tapi kebanyakan payah.

308
00:15:58,123 --> 00:15:59,708
Dan aku suka Devi.

309
00:15:59,792 --> 00:16:01,418
Bukan berarti harus jadi pacarku.

310
00:16:01,502 --> 00:16:02,461
Jadikan saja.

311
00:16:02,962 --> 00:16:05,047
Dengar, aku tak mau terdengar sok,

312
00:16:05,130 --> 00:16:06,507
tapi aku keren,

313
00:16:07,174 --> 00:16:10,970
sedangkan dia dikenal berkompetisi
di Lomba Mengeja Nasional.

314
00:16:11,804 --> 00:16:13,889
- Astaga.
- Kenapa?

315
00:16:14,556 --> 00:16:15,724
Kau berengsek.

316
00:16:16,600 --> 00:16:18,852
- Tidak.
- Ya, kau berengsek.

317
00:16:19,561 --> 00:16:23,107
Rebecca, dengar. Kami berciuman sekali.

318
00:16:23,190 --> 00:16:24,692
Aku tak perlu menikahinya.

319
00:16:24,775 --> 00:16:27,236
Juga, ibunya menyebutku bodoh.

320
00:16:27,319 --> 00:16:29,571
Aku tak butuh energi negatif begitu
dalam hidupku.

321
00:16:30,572 --> 00:16:32,574
Kau takut dia lebih pintar darimu?

322
00:16:33,117 --> 00:16:34,034
Tidak.

323
00:16:34,451 --> 00:16:36,161
Kau tak sopan, Rebecca.

324
00:16:36,245 --> 00:16:38,747
Yah, jika kau mengabaikan Devi,

325
00:16:39,123 --> 00:16:40,874
berarti kau memang bodoh.

326
00:16:46,630 --> 00:16:49,133
ANAK-ANAK YANG EMANSIPASI
DARI ORANG TUA MEREKA

327
00:16:50,009 --> 00:16:51,427
Hei, ada tamu.

328
00:16:52,970 --> 00:16:55,097
Kamar macam apa ini?

329
00:16:55,514 --> 00:16:56,932
Kenapa mereka kemari?

330
00:16:57,558 --> 00:16:59,351
Aku sedang tak ingin dikunjungi.

331
00:16:59,435 --> 00:17:01,729
Ini rumahku, aku bebas
mengundang siapa pun,

332
00:17:02,187 --> 00:17:05,024
