Kami pun merindukanmu, Devi.

362
00:18:32,111 --> 00:18:33,779
Mau nongkrong kapan-kapan?

363
00:18:36,281 --> 00:18:38,033
Ya, boleh juga.

364
00:18:38,826 --> 00:18:40,619
Besok kami kabari.

365
00:18:43,372 --> 00:18:45,332
Hei. Tugas kalian belum beres.

366
00:18:47,167 --> 00:18:48,502
Bujuk dia menaburkannya.

367
00:18:48,919 --> 00:18:50,504
Aku lupa tujuan kami.

368
00:18:50,587 --> 00:18:53,257
Kau memanipulasi pikiran kami
seperti Jedi.

369
00:18:53,340 --> 00:18:57,219
Ya, tapi ucapanku tadi serius.
Aku sungguh merindukan kalian.

370
00:18:57,302 --> 00:18:59,805
Ya, tapi kau tetap harus pergi ke Malibu.

371
00:18:59,888 --> 00:19:01,723
Agar ibuku bisa mengirimku ke India?

372
00:19:01,807 --> 00:19:03,475
Bukan itu alasanmu tak mau pergi.

373
00:19:04,101 --> 00:19:07,354
Kau tak mau pergi
karena enggan berpisah dengan ayahmu.

374
00:19:08,230 --> 00:19:09,898
Tapi kau harus.

375
00:19:11,817 --> 00:19:12,734
Aku belum siap.

376
00:19:15,696 --> 00:19:18,365
Kau siap. Kau pasti bisa.

377
00:19:19,074 --> 00:19:20,242
Kau harus pergi.

