432
00:22:17,044 --> 00:22:18,879
Kita tak bisa lakukan ini tanpa Devi.

433
00:22:20,464 --> 00:22:22,758
Tunggu! Hei!

434
00:22:24,634 --> 00:22:27,554
Jangan buang abu suamimu ke air!

435
00:22:30,307 --> 00:22:31,808
Itu John McEnroe?

436
00:22:33,894 --> 00:22:36,730
- Terima kasih banyak, Pak McEnroe.
- Tak masalah, Nak.

437
00:22:36,813 --> 00:22:39,733
Beri ayahmu perpisahan yang layak, ya?
